Subject: [PATCH] Use the dynamic CRT (/MD) on desktop Windows to match UE

V8's non-component desktop default is the static CRT (/MT); UE uses the dynamic
CRT (/MD). Mismatch -> LNK2038 RuntimeLibrary errors. Switch the default.

Path: build/config/win/BUILD.gn  (in the v8 'build' sub-repo)
--- a/build/config/win/BUILD.gn
+++ b/build/config/win/BUILD.gn
@@ config("default_crt") {
       configs = [ ":dynamic_crt" ]
     } else {
-      # Desktop Windows: static CRT.
-      configs = [ ":static_crt" ]
+      # Desktop Windows: dynamic CRT (/MD) to match Unreal Engine's runtime.
+      configs = [ ":dynamic_crt" ]
     }
   }
 }
